<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Modern Mixology Masterclasses</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/terminal.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/layout.css">
</head>
<body>

<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="terminal-container">
    <header class="dashboard-header">
        <h1>Welcome Back, <%= username %></h1>
        <p>The laboratory instruments are calibrated and awaiting your directives.</p>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="field-guide-section">
            <h2 class="guide-section-title">🔬 The Alchemist's Field Guide</h2>

            <div class="guide-grid">
                <div class="guide-card">
                    <h3 class="guide-card-title">📊 Stratification</h3>
                    <p class="guide-card-text">Manipulates liquid sugar weight (Brix scale) and alcohol densities to build distinct, un-mixed floating layers inside a single glassware vessel.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="guide-card">
                    <h3 class="guide-card-title">🔮 Encapsulation</h3>
                    <p class="guide-card-text">Employs calcium alginate gel cross-linking to trap liquid payloads inside fragile spheres that burst with explosive flavor clarity upon consumption.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="guide-card">
                    <h3 class="guide-card-title">🧪 Acid-Adjustment</h3>
                    <p class="guide-card-text">Alters the chemical pH balance of standard organic juices with precise powder vectors, synthesizing the high-acidity characteristics of citrus targets.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="guide-card">
                    <h3 class="guide-card-title">🌿 Botanical Alchemy</h3>
                    <p class="guide-card-text">Accelerates solvent extraction to isolate essential oils and organic chemical compounds from root and herbal matrices into custom aromatics.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <h2 class="dashboard-section-heading">The Main Stage: Theatrics</h2>

        <div class="module-grid grid-spaced">
            <a href="/modules/ph-shift" class="module-card">
                <h3>Botanical Alchemy</h3>
                <p>Master the interactive pH color shift using Butterfly Pea blossoms and citrus.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/modules/spherification" class="module-card">
                <h3>Encapsulation</h3>
                <p>Use sodium alginate to turn liquid modifiers into bursting, edible caviar.</p>
            </a>
        </div>

        <h2 class="dashboard-section-heading">The Prep Lab: Foundations</h2>

        <div class="module-grid grid-spaced">
            <a href="/modules/density" class="module-card">
                <h3>Density & Stratification</h3>
                <p>Learn the mechanics of floating spirits to create striking visual gradients.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/modules/acid" class="module-card">
                <h3>Acid-Adjustment</h3>
                <p>Engineer citrus profiles, turning simple juices into a perfectly balanced backbone.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/modules/pantry" class="module-card">
                <h3>The Pantry Engine</h3>
                <p>Select your available reagents and let the AI formulate a custom molecular protocol.</p>
            </a>
        </div>

        <h2 class="dashboard-section-heading archives-heading">The Archives: Record & Review</h2>

        <div class="module-grid">
            <a href="/modules/journal" class="module-card">
                <h3>Laboratory Journal</h3>
                <p>Access your personal grimoire. Review successfully formulated protocols, chemical syntheses, and past alchemical discoveries.</p>
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>
</div>

<div id="tour-overlay" class="tour-overlay hidden">
    <div class="tour-modal">
        <div class="tour-header">
            <span class="tour-step-badge" id="tour-counter">1/4</span>
            <button id="tour-close" class="tour-close-btn">&times;</button>
        </div>
        <h3 id="tour-title" class="tour-title">Welcome</h3>
        <p id="tour-text" class="tour-text">Tour text goes here.</p>
        <div class="tour-actions">
            <button id="tour-next" class="tour-btn">Next Sequence</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="/js/tour-engine.js"></script>

</body>
</html>